com.sirqul.sdk.interfaces

Interface ISirqulExecutor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SirqulExecutor

    public interface ISirqulExecutor
    The Interface IServiceExecutor. This is a required parameter on any SirqulTask execution, as it contains the call to execute(), which you'll implement with a call to a Sirqul API.
